{"tid":367240,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"用咩工具幫狗處理牙石?","createTime":"2017-08-20T15:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T03:56:37.000Z","uid":75256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2d0d14251e1b9477b8089ae1844bd90cc0d14f","tid":367240,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"琴日帶麻糬去打針 順便body check, 醫生話佢有牙石要清。本來屋企有支清牙石藥水, 但佢好似抗拒唔肯飲加左藥水嘅水。大家用咩預防/清除牙石方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補圖, 呢位係麻糬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l09ceg76\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl09ceg76&h=1013caab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vuc9k3wx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvuc9k3wx&h=e35bf81d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e71cc101a524bfc97a259ebd628935afd7a4450","tid":367240,"uid":112494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"比寵物美容搞"},{"pid":"686c0a447885b852dd0bfae2132b4c8ecda72ba8","tid":367240,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比寵物美容搞</blockquote><br />\n要搵信得過 之前上網睇到過有上門洗牙出事<br />\n不過都係一兩單 小心d揀就得<br />\n牙石粉有冇試過？"},{"pid":"8e721d6f412d9e13fe20b5ada96400bf3ebfa658","tid":367240,"uid":112494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比寵物美容搞</blockquote><br />\n要搵信得過 之前上網睇到過有上門洗牙出事<br />\n不過都係一兩單 小心d揀就得<br />\n牙石粉有冇試過？</blockquote><br />\n點樣出事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f759515f0b84170ff8d01baa6532f0dac57dda7","tid":367240,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比寵物美容搞</blockquote><br />\n要搵信得過 之前上網睇到過有上門洗牙出事<br />\n不過都係一兩單 小心d揀就得<br />\n牙石粉有冇試過？</blockquote><br />\n點樣出事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n免麻醉洗牙吖嘛，被洗牙嗰個整到窒息死左<br />\n因為狗會驚會反抗，除非你隻狗咩人都摸得又唔亂郁<br />\n<br />\n洗牙都係醫生專業啲"},{"pid":"a1689eef2fcb129af2288a95d0900a3b26004fca","tid":367240,"uid":109961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"好撚得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db01b391d2f82bf4b7bf3db4fe881a9bc754cc7","tid":367240,"uid":92325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"去睇獸醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd去牙石藥水咁恐怖都敢用"},{"pid":"8621369b473fdb047b1637f516ae962aac9c1f56","tid":367240,"uid":89691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:39:59.000Z","msg":"狗用牙刷"},{"pid":"620d032b90d88fd60b537214eecabce671340031","tid":367240,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:30:32.000Z","msg":"個樣好驚青"},{"pid":"ebac532e367c7143fd34f51bda3eeaa84aa920c8","tid":367240,"uid":53180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"每日刷牙可以預防"},{"pid":"026144c836753759f1cfb967b18f9b1fec2ca645","tid":367240,"uid":67272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:56:37.000Z","msg":"每日刷牙，用牙膏<br />\n唔用牙膏，抹身時幫佢抹下對牙俾佢咬毛巾<br />\n我會放潔齒水(可飲用)落水到唔會太大味<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我個隻係貓黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}